CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: David L. Lawrence speaking at podium outdoors in Oakland, with military or police band seated behind him, University of Pittsburgh's Cathedral of Learning, and Carnegie Mellon buildings in background
